name: Milk Bottle Tee
description:
This design was originally going to be the logo. But I later decided that it was too complicated to fill that position. The idea of placing the heart into the milk bottle was inspired by the Milk Jones motto,"Heart & Individuality." You should put your heart into everything you do.

This shirt is not form fitting, instead it flows across the body.
Poly viscose 65/35,30 single 3.7oz/yd,125 gm/m

name: Power Tee
description:
"Power" is my representation of female empowerment. A woman has the right to be as aggressive,provocative and as sexy as she wants, because at the end if the day she is still a force to be reckon with. She is POWERFUL.

This shirt is not form fitting, instead it flows across the body.
Poly viscose 65/35,30 single 3.7oz/yd,125 gm/m
